ry\">surgery</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of synergism \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/synergism\">synergism</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of synergy \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/synergy\">synergy</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of thaumaturge \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/thaumaturge\">thaumaturge</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of work \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/work\">work</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of wright \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/wright\">wright</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of wrought \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/wrought\">wrought</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of zymurgy \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/zymurgy\">zymurgy</a>。</p><p>它是假设的源头，其存在的证据由以下单词提供： <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">ergon</i>（希腊语）“工作”， <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">orgia</i>（希腊语）“宗教表演”； <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">gorc</i>（亚美尼亚语）“工作”； <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">vareza</i>（阿维斯陀语）“工作，活动”； <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">waurkjan</i>（哥特语）， <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">wyrcan</i>（古英语）“工作”， <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">weorc</i>（古英语）“行为，动作，已完成的事情”； <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">yrka</i>（古诺尔斯语）“工作，生效”。</p>"
